1)git checkout <branchname> 

2) nano /var/www/html/path/to/file/sample.blade.php

3) git add .

4) git commit -m "tesing new changes"

5) git push origin <branchname> 

================ BIT BUCKKET===========

6) check your latest commit changes

7) create a pull request from branch to dev-ops branch

8) go to pull request > open related request and merge the file to dev-ops branch

============= IF Confilicts arised ===========

9) git pull origin <masterbranch> dev-ops

10) open sample.blade.php file and remove the conflicts and follow the same steps 3 to 8 again

=========== Create a new issue in jira and create a new branch in that issue======

11) in local  git fetch && git checkout (new branch name)

git status  : check whether ur in new branch or not  

git checkout new_branch_name : Move form one branch to another branch.

now perform steps 2,3,4,5.
